latestIgtvVideos.title: 2 Step Hair Spa at home // DIY hair care Routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey Everyone! Happy Weekend.
So recently I came across the brand @amrutamofficial while searching for Ayurvedic Hair Care Range & I ended up trying their Hair Care Range specifically Kuntal care do-it-yourself Hair Spa + Herbal Shampoo, it's been more than 4 weeks I have used these products & I was just amazed by the results I got.

There is less hair fall,more shine to my Hair and my hair looks & feels healthy. So In today's video, I am not only going to show you how I do a simple weekend 2 Step hair spa at home but will be also reviewing Amrutam products & talking about their ayurvedic Ingredients and the benefits.

Products used 
1) Kuntal Care Do It Yourself Hair Spa.
2) Kuntal Care Herbal Shampoo.

They were kind enough to provide me with a coupon code : "SHALINI15"

💗
 #KuntalCare #AmrutamFamily #WithMyAmrutam 
I hope this video was helpful.❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Quarantine & Don't Rush 🔥
My Visit to Forest Essential Store | Ayurvedic Skin Care India
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Recently, I visited the Forest Essentials store @forestessentials at DB mall Bhopal @dbcitymall for one of kind experience! I not only explored the store but I learned a lot more about what the Luxury Ayurvedic skin care brand has to offer. I had a fun interactive session with Dr. Akansha from Team FE, she told me about my Dosha and how I can choose my skin care according to my Dosha I.E.  Kapha. 
Thank you FE for having me!
#forestessentials #forestessentialsindia #ayurvedicskincare

latestPosts.caption:
my skin in 30s 🤌
..
I had struggled with hormonal acne, dark spots and pigmentation in my 20s and I think I finally understood how to take care of my skin in my 30s and keep them healthy & supple

- sunscreen is my no. 1 anti aging product ) 

- the new ingredient MELASYL in the  New L’Oréal Paris Glycolic Bright Serum has been game changing to reduce dark spot & together with glycolic acid it helps to brightens the skin

- Tretinion is my bestie for cell turnover & to helps to reduce fine lines & wrinkles

- Ceramide / Hyaluronic to prevent water loss from the skin.
